{"tid":910514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【女警開槍案】中槍男一度命危，家屬記者會申訴","createTime":"2018-11-21T08:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T13:37:44.000Z","uid":20896,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c38e2e86b5662980b2c9f864d718e6024dd41ae6","tid":910514,"uid":20896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"一名陀槍師姐本月初上班繁忙時間，與男同袍在港鐵深水埗站大堂截查一名有襲警前科男子時，男子突取出鎅刀，並持刀衝向女警企圖施襲，女警感生命受威脅及在警告無效下，開一槍將男子轟倒，男子左腹中槍其後送院搶救。事隔兩周後，傷者家屬在民主黨立法會涂謹申的陪同下，於下午4時30分<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申 又做乜鳩啊"},{"pid":"397ad79cec0ef45bce649dbc421e1eeb25cc289f","tid":910514,"uid":201604,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:47:43.000Z","msg":"逃緊生"},{"pid":"316f5a80a0962154e55d5150a1404e1a761e6cfa","tid":910514,"uid":202278,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22f1570b55a00a4e2c0238ac54928d11ee105c09","tid":910514,"uid":12021,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63421e265b6ffd03aa9a52d2a5dad56029733609","tid":910514,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:56:23.000Z","msg":"做埋啲吃力不討好既on9野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777ce33e8d52ebc765cedcffa17f30bccd1153f0","tid":910514,"uid":108347,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"無啦啦抆刀隊人都唔開得槍咩"},{"pid":"ef297f5d9af47d44a04ea3eff94eb15d178fd7b6","tid":910514,"uid":20896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁on9"},{"pid":"8b8536d1abe815d8a903cc8059079f84533122ea","tid":910514,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"22f1570b55a00a4e2c0238ac54928d11ee105c09","tid":910514,"uid":12021,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:02:10.000Z",